---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Use | AskDaveDowntown"
  description="Terms of use for AskDaveDowntown website."
  noindex={true}
>
  <Section>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-ink">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

      <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing AskDaveDowntown, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use this site.</p>

      <h2>General Information Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>All content on this site - including blog posts, guides, area profiles, and Q&A answers - is provided for <strong>general informational purposes only</strong>. It does not constitute personalised legal, financial, tax, or investment advice. The information published here reflects general market conditions and publicly available data at the time of writing and may not be current or applicable to your specific circumstances.</p>

      <h2>Not a Substitute for Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>Real estate transactions involve significant financial and legal commitments. Before making any property purchase, sale, or investment decision, you should consult with qualified professionals including licensed real estate agents, legal advisors, mortgage specialists, and tax consultants who can assess your individual situation.</p>

      <h2>Regulatory Compliance</h2>
      <p>David Buckley is a licensed real estate broker registered with the Real Estate Regulatory Agency (RERA) under the Dubai Land Department (DLD), operating through Paragon Properties. All professional activity is conducted in accordance with RERA regulations and the Dubai Real Estate Institute (DREI) Code of Ethics. This website is an educational and informational resource and does not constitute a property listing or advertisement for specific units. Any property-specific marketing is conducted separately in compliance with RERA's Trakheesi advertising permit system.</p>

      <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p>While every effort is made to ensure accuracy, property values, fees, government regulations, visa requirements, mortgage rates, and market conditions are subject to change without notice. All figures, statistics, and regulatory information should be independently verified with the relevant authorities - including the Dubai Land Department, RERA, the UAE Central Bank, and the Federal Authority for Identity, Citizenship, Customs and Port Security (ICP) - before making any decisions.</p>

      <h2>No Guarantees on Returns</h2>
      <p>Any rental yield figures, capital appreciation data, or investment return projections mentioned on this site are based on historical or general market data and are not guarantees of future performance. Property investment carries risk, including the potential for loss of capital.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>This site may contain links to third-party websites for informational purposes. AskDaveDowntown is not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of external websites.</p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on this site - text, images, and tools - is the property of AskDaveDowntown. You may not reproduce or distribute content without prior written consent.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>AskDaveDowntown and David Buckley are not liable for any losses, damages, or costs arising from reliance on information provided on this site. Use of this site is entirely at your own risk.</p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United Arab Emirates and the Emirate of Dubai. Any disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts of Dubai.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email dave.buckley@paragonproperties.ae.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
